Title: Slow cooker

Notes

HMV questions
    HMV make it fast and easy
        Make a collection of easy recipes with few steps and good and nutritious food
    HMV have food for more than 1 day
        Have different recipes require the same ingredients for the ability to prep beforehand
    HMV find a time to eat and consider different work hours
        Set a time to eat at the latest time off work since they don't need to eat early
    HMV make sure the food doesn't get boring
        provide enough recipes so the food doesn't get boring
    HMV solve sudden complications
        have a frozen backup meal or a planed takeout solution

ideas

A app/website with recipes, time to make, whats needed to make it all together
    it should only be recipes that are easy to follow and simple to cook

    the option to insert a time where you want to eat so it can give you a time to start cooking or a time to live after cooking it if you want to prep for more than one day

    when choosing a recipe have more options that use the same ingredients to reduce the need to shop daily to cook


